oes are recommended for walking across campus and in the oak grove there is debris from the trees in the diploma ceremony site we recommend that guests eat a hearty breakfast and pack a snack light refreshments will be available for purchase at the stanford stadium a champagne and hors d oeuvres reception will follow the suse ceremony at 2 00 pm water will be available at both ceremony locations you may wish to bring your own water as well we regret that umbrellas will not be permitted at either ceremony as they would block the view of other guests smoking guidelines smoking is prohibited in outdoor locations where arranged seating fixed or temporary is provided for programs or events outdoor locations include but are not limited to the main quadrangle stanford stadium amphitheaters and courtyards commencement important information for graduating students guest information faculty information day of information for graduates speaker information june 12 2011 8 00am stanford stadium gates open for guests 9 30am stanford commencement ceremony 11 00am suse ceremony setup in west oval grove 12 30pm suse diploma ceremony 2 00pm reception in west oval grove stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
